**Raven** | Attribute
__Basics__
The Raven attribute is applied by the ravenkeeper. If one player with a raven visits a player with a raven from the same ravenkeeper, the ravenkeeper is informed at the end of the phase.

__Formalized__
On Starting:Starting: Set Counter to 1
On Visited [!Targeting]: 
• @Self->Counter > `0`:
  ‣ Decrement Counter
  ‣ Passive [End Phase]:
    ◦ Reveal `@Self was @VisitType` to #Ravenkeeper
